{
  "text": "The modified algorithm is called the optimized cutting plane algorithm (OCAS) [CITATION_1] , and it was shown that the number of iterations needed for convergence is the same order as that in [CITATION_2] . On the other hand, OCAS is reported to be much faster in numerical experiments than the algorithm proposed in [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
